I was testing what I've recently learnt, and decided to make this into my first map. shout out to Maharero, texture combinations of stage 1 were inspired from a stage in bhop_challenjour. map is about 4 minutes long if ran optimally. gl hf

- please note that this is my first map. I didn't put a lot of time into it and rushed it tbh, mostly trying to learn. I will probably make another long map in the future but will invest more time into it. and will have the level design, textures to be more unique.
